  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The model was revised in 2026 to incorporate updated impeller geometry tolerances and revised turbulence closure coefficients; however, the primary experimental hemolysis dataset bound to this assessment carries a dataVintage of 2018-03-15, predating the 2026 model revision. The narrative does not address re-validation against post-revision data, leaving an unacknowledged epistemic gap.",
