    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors assessed or flagged. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ demonstrates 95th-percentile hemolysis index below clinical threshold at nominal operating point. Assessment team accepted the package on the basis of the UQ results and the conservative hemolysis model, without noting that the primary experimental validation dataset (dataVintage 2018-03-15) predates the January 2026 model revision and has not been re-evaluated against the revised model predictions.",
